<h1>Avatars</h1>
<p>
	Avatars across Fandom should be circular with a 2px internal border.
</p>

<section>
	<h2 id="avatar-circle">Circle avatar</h2>

	{{#component-demo name='avatar'}}
		{{wds-avatar src=(concat rootURL 'images/FANDOM-Avatar.jpg') alt='user name' badge='admin'}}
		{{wds-avatar src=(concat rootURL 'images/FANDOM-Avatar.jpg') alt='user name' link='http://fandom.wikia.com'}}
		{{wds-avatar src='' alt='user name'}}
	{{/component-demo}}

	<h2>Parameters</h2>
	<div>
		<h3>HBS Properties</h3>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>src</strong> (string): path to the the icon</li>
			<li><strong>alt</strong> (string): alternative title</li>
			<li><strong>badge</strong> (string): if provided, badge will be displayed on top of avatar</li>
			<li><strong>link</strong> (string): if provided, avatar will be wrapped in <code class="format-code">&lt;a&gt;</code> tag and linked to url provided as value.</li>
		</ul>
	</div>

	<h2>Sizes and theming</h2>
	<p>Size and colors of avatar can be set via SCSS mixin <code class="format-code">wds-avatar</code>, for example

<pre class="hljs htmlbars"><code class="format-code">.wds-avatar {
	@include wds-avatar(30px, $color, $color-hover, $color-background);
}</code></pre>

	</p>
